      <title>交易员认为美联储立场更为鹰派，新兴市场外汇指数下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-slip-as-fed-signals-hawkish-rates-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美联储对明年利率走势发表强硬言论的影响，新兴市场货币指数在美元普遍走强的情况下延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-slip-as-fed-signals-hawkish-rates-outlook</guid>
